high_descs: Turn left, step forward, then right and go to the shelves against the wall.
Pick up the keys in the compartment.
Turn around and walk into the space in between the two beds to face the nightstand.
Places the keys in the lower center of the nightstand.
Turn around and walk out of the space, turn right, go to the foot of the bed and turn right. to face the bed
Pick up the keys in the lower shelf compartment on the left.
Return to the nightstand in between the two beds.
Place the keys on the nightstand to the left of the phone.
anns.task_desc: Find two sets of keys, place on nightstand.

high_descs: Turn left and walk forward, then turn right and walk up to the wooden shelving unit on the wall.
Pick up the set of keys off of the middle shelf.
Walk over to the nightstand in between the two beds.
Put the set of keys on the nightstand to the right of the pencil.
Turn around and walk towards the door, then hang a right and walk up to the shelving unit.
Pick up the set of keys off of the lower right shelf.
Walk back over to the nightstand in between the two beds.
Put the set of keys on the night stand to the left of the phone.
anns.task_desc: Move two sets of keys to a nightstand.

high_descs: walk forward and look up to face the top shelf on the wall.
Pick up the keys on the top shelf on the wall.
Turn right and walk between the beds to face the night stand.
Place the keys on the night stand.
Turn around and walk around the bed to the right to face the bottom right shelf on the wall.
Pick up the keys on the bottom right shelf on the wall.
Turn right and walk between the beds to face the night stand.
Place the keys on the night stand next to the first set of keys.
anns.task_desc: To place two sets of keys on the night stand between the beds.
